high_descs: Move forward and then right beside the couch. Turn right to face the short side of the couch.
Pick up the remote from the edge of the couch.
Carry the remote and turn to the right. Then left and face the coffee table on the left.
Place the remote on the center of the coffee table.
Turn to the left and then the left again to face the short side of the cabinet.
Pick up the remote that is close to the short side of the cabinet.
Carry the remote and turn to the left, and then right and face the coffee table on the left.
Place the remote on the coffee table, next to the other remote.
anns.task_desc: Move two remotes to the coffee table.

high_descs: Walk towards the wall, then turn right and walk over to the wall, turn right again to face the couch.
Pick up the remote off of the couch.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk to the side of the coffee table.
Put the remote on the coffee table in front of the rightmost laptop.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the wall, turn left again to face the television.
Pick up the remote off of the table.
Turn left and walk over to the coffee table.
Put the remote on the coffee table to the right of the remote that's already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two remotes to the coffee table.

high_descs: Go to the sofa
Pick up the remote
Go to the center table
Put the remote down
Go to the TV table
Pick up the remote
Go to the center table
Put the remote down on the table
anns.task_desc: Move two remotes to the center table
